  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Flex 的安装</title>

    <para>首先，修复某些回归测试:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="pre">patch -Np1 -i ../&flex-bison-patch;</userinput></screen>

    <para>准备 Flex 编译:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="configure">./configure --prefix=/usr             \
            --docdir=/usr/share/doc/flex-&flex-version;</userinput></screen>

    <para>编译包:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="make">make</userinput></screen>

    <para>要测试结果(约 0.5 SBU)，执行:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="test">make check</userinput></screen>

    <para>安装包:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="install">make install</userinput></screen>

    <para>有一些包预期在 <filename
    class="directory">/usr/lib</filename> 中查找
    <filename class="libraryfile">lex</filename> 库。为此创建一个符号链接账户:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="install">ln -sv libfl.a /usr/lib/libl.a</userinput></screen>

    <para>一些程序还不知道 <command>flex</command> ，而且尝试运行它的前任，<command>lex</command>。要支持那些程序，创建一个名为 <filename>lex</filename> 的封装器脚本，它会以 <command>lex</command> 模拟模式调用 <filename>flex</filename>:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="install">cat &gt; /usr/bin/lex &lt;&lt; "EOF"
<literal>#!/bin/sh
# Begin /usr/bin/lex

exec /usr/bin/flex -l "$@"

# End /usr/bin/lex</literal>
EOF
chmod -v 755 /usr/bin/lex</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 id="contents-flex" role="content">
    <title>Flex 的内容</title>

